<div class="teacher-header"><h1>Carly Chamberlain</h1><div class="sm"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/carly-chamberlain-15631661/"><svg class="icon icon-linkedin"><use xlink:href="#icon-linkedin"></use></svg><span>LinkedIn</span></a> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/siromaniwell/" title="Facebook"><svg class="icon icon-facebook2"><use xlink:href="#icon-facebook2"></use></svg><span>Facebook</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/siromaniwell" title="Twitter"><svg class="icon icon-twitter"><use xlink:href="#icon-twitter"></use></svg><span>Twitter</span></a></div></div><img src="images/teachers/bio-pages/carly-chamberlain.jpg" alt="Carly Chamberlain" class="w350fr"><p>Carly Chamberlain is an advanced body therapist, yoga teacher and trainer who has spent many years working in the complementary healthcare and global luxury spa industry.</p><p>Carly's combined experiences enable her to give a unique offering in the treatment of injuries and chronic conditions as well as educating on the importance of body and mind maintenance.</p><p>Carly trained at the Sivananda Yoga Vedanta in the Himalayas in 2012. This intensely disciplined experience transformed her outlook on life, reinforcing her passion for self preservation and healing.</p>